title: Rescue Rangers episode 1
description:
Here is the first episode in the Disney Rescue Rangers.  I think the media came from a DVR dump.  I do not have a constant link to the internet so here is a link to the rest if it is not on the torrent network.



The files are VGA size and encoded with H.264.  I chopped off the introductions because the little captions were in Spanish but the whole video is in English.  Also the introduction reminds me too much of a happy glee club singing in a high school band.
